@HEADER-COMMENT@

@HEADER@
Group:	System/YaST
BuildRequires:	blocxx-devel docbook-xsl-stylesheets doxygen gcc-c++ libgcrypt-devel libxcrypt-devel libxslt perl-XML-Writer sgml-skel yast2-core-devel yast2-devtools
